7:59.000Z","msg":"位於<span class=\"red\">大埔墟寶鄉街2號</span>，樓高20層，地下及1樓提供青年空間服務，2至3樓提供多用途空間、共用廚房及洗衣房等附屬設施，而4至19樓則合共提供70個<span class=\"red\">單人單位，</span>面積為<span class=\"red\">187至232平方呎，</span><span class=\"red\">每月租金為4248至5831港元;</span> 2個<span class=\"green\">雙人單位，面積為398平方呎，每月租金為8670至8711港元</span>; 以及<span class=\"blue\">2個三人單位，每人可享155至189平方呎的獨立空間，共享160平方呎的客廳，每人每月租金約為4606港元。</span><br />\n<br />\n宿舍首次租期為2年，如獲續租，總租期合計不得超過5年。申請者必需為18至30歲香港永久性居民，單人申請者月入不超過2.1萬港元，總資產不超過36.4萬港元，並未在香港持有物業。<br />\n<br />\n中籤者需於網上提交如住址證明、資產證明和最少3個月的薪金證明等文件，以及出席面談以作核實及評審。另外，倘申請人持有單人公屋戶籍，成功入住後則需放棄該戶籍，但不影響其公屋輪候資格。"},{"pid":"e873bb1e2d1c92c8cfbf1e572d211f28d93e6d7c","tid":2505774,"uid":68646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:39:53.000Z","msg":"同定仔一齊住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e4d17afe03a4920bb109e2feed415f72a0eca6","tid":2505774,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e873bb1e2d1c92c8cfbf1e572d211f28d93e6d7c","tid":2505774,"uid":68646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:39:53.000Z","msg":"同定仔一齊住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:41:39.000Z","msg":"是<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e9181377d4412fc73636a94b6d0a8e09ccccbe7","tid":2505774,"uid":128993,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d87c011afe2b2f07cee5fa164945862f5e897f86","tid":2505774,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b8d20bf576946ed6de35ff8e42b0b15d35075ae","tid":2505774,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4cce0544b5e851035e37969109f4183bc1bff90b","tid":2505774,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T01:44:30.000Z","msg":"大埔<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:05:25.000Z","msg":"是<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}